        <updateDate>2021-01-15T16:55:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Preserving Patient Access to Home Infusion Act</b></p> <p>This bill specifically includes pharmacy services and certain self-administered drugs as part of covered home infusion therapy under Medicare, and specifies that certain payment components still apply regardless of whether or not a qualified supplier is physically present in the beneficiary's home. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
